--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
DATA LICENSES
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

The datasets consumed by this pipeline retain their upstream licenses:

- IBGE municipality boundaries and Censo 2022 tabulations:
    Public domain / Creative Commons Zero (CC0).
    Source: https://www.ibge.gov.br/

- CNES (Cadastro Nacional de Estabelecimentos de Saude):
    Public domain, distributed by DATASUS / Ministerio da Saude.
    Source: https://cnes.datasus.gov.br/

- INEP (Catalogo de Escolas / Censo Escolar):
    Public domain, distributed by INEP / Ministerio da Educacao.
    Source: https://www.gov.br/inep/pt-br/acesso-a-informacao/dados-abertos

- OpenStreetMap extracts via Geofabrik:
    Open Database License (ODbL) v1.0.
    Attribution: (c) OpenStreetMap contributors.
    Source: https://download.geofabrik.de/
